    narr:Narrative_SelfHostingEnablesNewProducts


      skos:broader narr:ExpansionPathway ;
      skos:prefLabel "Self-Hosting Unlocks Cost-Prohibitive Product Ideas" ;
      skos:note "Moving from per-token API costs to fixed server costs opens product ideas previously cost-prohibitive: SMS/WhatsApp interface to organizational memory, always-on agents holding full perspective in context, batch re-extraction when ontology evolves, eval at scale across full memory corpus. Scarlet: 'if payment for inference was server cost instead of API spend, that would not only save many hundreds of dollars a month (and many thousands post launch) but it would open up a ton of product ideas i haven't been doing because they're cost prohibitive (ie sms with inference behind it or agents backed by large perspectives where every response has the full perspective as context).'" ;
      narr:theme "Fixed server costs vs. per-token API spend is not just a cost reduction — it unlocks an entirely different product surface area including SMS, always-on agents, and eval at scale" .

    narr:Claim_SMSAgentsNowViable
      a narr:Claim ;

      skos:note "Self-hosted inference makes SMS/WhatsApp interface to organizational memory and always-on agents holding full perspective in context viable. These were previously cost-prohibitive under per-token API pricing. Fixed server costs change the economics fundamentally." ;
      narr:aboutNode narr:Narrative_SelfHostingEnablesNewProducts ;
      narr:hasConvictionLevel narr:Conviction_Boulder ;
      narr:supports narr:Narrative_SelfHostingEnablesNewProducts .

